<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>JOBUSS Tech</title>
    <%- include('partials/head.ejs') %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="resources/css/style.css">
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap');

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background: url('https://images.pexels.com/photos/29738255/pexels-photo-29738255/free-photo-of-representacion-abstracta-de-un-paisaje-urbano-en-3d-con-degradado.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=2');
            background-size: cover;
            background-attachment: fixed;
            background-position: center;
            color: #ffffff;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            overflow: hidden; /* Evitar desbordamientos */
        }

        .container {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 700px;
            width: 90%;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 120, 150, 0.5);
            animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-in-out;
            max-height: 90vh; /* Limitar altura */
            overflow: auto; /* Permitir desplazamiento si es necesario */
        }

        .container h1 {
            font-size: 4vw;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff758c, #ff7eb3);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            animation: glow 2s infinite alternate;
        }

        .container p {
            font-size: 2vw;
            opacity: 0.9;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .buttons a {
            display: inline-block;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 14px 30px;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: 0.3s ease-in-out;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .btn-login {
            background: #e78aa9;
            color: #121212;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px #e78aa9;
        }

        .btn-login:hover {
            background: #ff9ecf;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px #ff9ecf;
        }

        .btn-register {
            background: none;
            color: #fcdbff;
            border: 2px solid #e78aa9;
        }

        .btn-register:hover {
            background: #ecb7e7;
            color: #121212;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px #ecb7e7;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; }
            to { opacity: 1; }
        }

        @keyframes glow {
            from {
                text-shadow: 0px 0px 5px rgba(255, 120, 150, 0.7);
            }
            to {
                text-shadow: 0px 0px 15px rgba(255, 120, 150, 1);
            }
        }

        /* Media Queries */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container h1 {
                font-size: 5vw;
            }

            .container p {
                font-size: 3.5vw;
            }

            .buttons a {
                font-size: 16px;
                padding: 12px 25px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .container h1 {
                font-size: 6vw;
            }

            .container p {
                font-size: 4vw;
            }

            .buttons a {
                font-size: 14px;
                padding: 10px 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <h1>Bienvenido a JOBUSS Tech</h1>
    <p>Innovación y creatividad para impulsar la tecnología. Conectamos ideas con soluciones para el futuro.</p>

    <div class="buttons">

        <a href="/login" class="btn-login">Iniciar Sesión</a>
        <a href="/registro" class="btn-register">Registrarse</a>    
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
